Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class WorkLoadDescription

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.VisualizationObject
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.WorkLoadDescription
Direct Known Subclasses:
WorkLoad
public class WorkLoadDescription
extends VisualizationObject
Reads the input file, whose name is passed as input parameter to the constructor, and builds a Description object based on the contents. Each line of the file is an entry (string) in the Description object.
Version:
1.4 Fall 2022
Author:
